                        BC PNP has received only <strong>5,254 nominations</strong> for 2026—significantly less than the 9,000 requested. Competition will be fiercer than ever. Read our latest <a href="/articles/bc-pnp-february-2026-draw-results-analysis" class="underline font-bold">February 2026 Draw Analysis</a> for current scoring trends.
                    </p>
